The paper focuses on improving the performance of neural network-based Video Description/Caption, Visual Question Answering (VQA) and Audio Visual Scene-aware Dialog (AVSD) through multi-modality fusion technologies. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV), Natural Language Processing (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories of arXiv CS.
